title: The Nature Of Things Collection 3 10of12 The Cholesterol Questio
description: The Cholesterol Question is a hard-hitting investigation into the heart of cholesterol's controversial journey, from essential biological substance to Public Enemy Number One and possible rehab. It's a villain that's simple to understand, easy to implicate and, we thought, easy to medicate. But it's a story almost stranger than fiction. At Stanford University, Dr. Christopher Gardner reveals the debatable science behind our assault on dietary fat and cholesterol - a massive intervention that many believe only made us fatter and sicker
